  "topicId": "ch5-light",
  "type": "short_answer",
  "subtopic": "Exercise 5.1",
  "question": "2) (a)What is meant by reflection?",
  "answer": "The phenomenon of bouncing back of light to the same medium after striking on a\nsurface is called as reflection of light.\n(b) State the laws of reflection?\nA. First law:- Angle of incidence is equal to the angle of reflection i.e. ˂i=˂r.\n Second law:- The incident ray, the reflected ray and the normal at the point of\n incidence lie on a same plane."
