  "question": "1.a) What is energy?",
  "answer": "Energy is the capacity to do work.\nb) What do you understand by work?\nAns. work is said to be done when a force applied on a body causes a displacement in its\nown direction.\nc) Is the energy spent on thinking or talking a kind of work? Give reason for your answer.\nAns. No, because of no displacement of the body."
