  "subtopic": "Exercise 4.3",
  "question": "7. Briefly describe nuclear energy and its\nI) one use\nii) one misuse",
  "answer": "The energy produced during the breaking of a heavy nucleus or making of a nucleus is\ncalled nuclear energy.\nOne use is it can be used in nuclear power plants to produce electricity.\nOne misuse is it can be used in atom bombs to cause massive destruction."
